Sinopsis 
Walking the tight rope between circus and theater, Cirque du Soleil combines awe-inspiring acrobatics with elaborate lighting design, dazzling costumes, and engagingly moody live music. With QUIDAM the ensemble weaves a narrative of a young girl&#039;s adventures in an alternate universe into their surreal, death-defying performance.
